      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 39
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a museum-grade specimen featuring the legendary S54 inline-six, renowned for its high-pressure VANOS system and individual throttle bodies. The engine exhibits perfect compression and has received proactive rod bearing replacement. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission to a GKN-sourced limited-slip differential. The chassis is structurally immaculate, featuring documented subframe reinforcement to ensure long-term torsional rigidity. Every bushing and damper remains within factory tolerances, providing the telepathic steering response and linear power delivery these icons are known for. Finished in a deep luster with no evidence of panel gap misalignment or oxidative wear, this is a turn-key collector-quality vehicle.",
      "price": 43500.0,
